snippet.title: TEALERLAND - Video Teaser
snippet.description:
TEALERLAND IS OUT NOW: https://gamejolt.com/games/TEALERLAND/466109
A short, sneak peek teaser of gameplay from the full version of TEALERLAND, out now!

See TEALERLAND's new look revealed for the first time, as well as some new mechanics & features.
More info is coming later this year.
